Class DefineVideoStreamTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.Tag
      • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.CharacterTag
        • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.DefineVideoStreamTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICharacterTag, ITag

    public class DefineVideoStreamTag
extends CharacterTag
    Represents a DefineVideoStream tag in a SWF file.

    DefineVideoStream defines a video character that can later be placed on the display list.
